name: PHCollectionListSubtype
desc: Major distinctions between kinds of collection list, used by the collectionListSubtype property and fetchCollectionLists(with:subtype:options:), fetchMomentLists(with:containingMoment:options:), and fetchMomentLists(with:options:) methods.

items.name: case momentListCluster
items.desc: The collection list is a moment cluster, grouping several related moments.

items.name: case momentListYear
items.desc: The collection list is a moment year, grouping all moments from one or more calendar years.

items.name: case regularFolder
items.desc: The collection list is a folder containing albums or other folders.

items.name: case smartFolderEvents
items.desc: The collection list is a smart folder containing one or more Events synced from iPhoto.

items.name: case smartFolderFaces
items.desc: The collection list is a smart folder containing one or more Faces synced from iPhoto.

items.name: case any
items.desc: Use this value to fetch collection lists of all possible subtypes.
